	Every artist is invited to create these LoveCoins.
	When creating these LoveCoins, the artist&#x27;s love flows into this note, which means that it has
	already have a value. Someone created it with love, which unfortunately we don&#x27;t say about the banknotes. 
	Someone has made an effort to create these notes and to make them counterfeit-proof,
	but actually they&#x27;re just copies. The EUR and Dollars are actually worthless. 
	Only we humans give them a value because we accept it as a form of payment. 
&lt;/p&gt;
